metadata.formula: MLI = Median Income / Cost of Living

methodology.costs: BLS Consumer Expenditure Survey baseline × CPI deflators × BEA RPPs

interpretation.1.0: Income exactly covers expenses (paycheck to paycheck)

notes: Cost of Living accounts for actual inflation 2008-2023
Middle class = Q3 (50th percentile) household income

2012_2023.interpretation: Cost of living increased 31%, purchasing power increased 14%
